title: Visual Inspector

creator: Percepthor
descriptionHtml:
With Visual Inspector you will be able to verify that the operation of your business is being carried out optimally where it matters: in the field of work.

Our system allows you to validate through images taken by your own operators that the work is being done in the right way, in the right place and at the right time.

The evidence of images in the operation becomes data to be evaluated at the moment or later through your business intelligence processes.

We have the most flexible and scalable system on the market, which allows us to manage from a small team in the field with only one market channel to thousands of users with a complex organizational structure, multiple geographies and different customer profiles.
descriptionShort: Artificial intelligence applied to any kind of visual inspection.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Multiple map improvements and UI fixes.

descriptionHtml:
With Visual Inspector you will be able to verify that the operation of your business is being carried out optimally where it matters: in the field of work.

Our system allows you to validate through images taken by your own operators that the work is being done in the right way, in the right place and at the right time.

The evidence of images in the operation becomes data to be evaluated at the moment or later through your business intelligence processes.

We have the most flexible and scalable system on the market, which allows us to manage from a small team in the field with only one market channel to thousands of users with a complex organizational structure, multiple geographies and different customer profiles.
descriptionShort: Artificial intelligence applied to any kind of visual inspection.
